ECB Said to Be Purchasing Italian, Spanish Bonds to Cap Yields

-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 
2011-10-03T08:28:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/ecb-said-to-be-purchasing-italian-spanish-bonds-to-cap-yields.html
The  European Central Bank  bought
Italian and Spanish government bonds, according to three people
with knowledge of the transactions, who asked not to be
identified because the deals are confidential.  A spokesman for the ECB declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucy Meakin in  London  at 
 lmeakin1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Daniel Tilles at   dtilles@bloomberg.net . 